# Squad-bundle templates directory — generated artifact exclusions.
#
# Template instances are created by adopters via `cp *.template -> domains/<new>/<artifact>`
# followed by sed token substitution. The resulting domain files are committed
# to .claude/skills/domains/<slug>/ as canonical artifacts. This .gitignore
# prevents intermediate generated files from being accidentally staged here.
#
# Template-vs-instance distinction:
#   *.template  — source template (committed, tracked)
#   <artifact>  — generated instance (committed in skills/domains/, NOT here)

# Scratch / intermediate files from token substitution passes
*.bak
*.tmp

# Generated instance artifacts that should live in skills/domains/, not here
team-personas.md
pitfalls.yaml
task-chains.yaml

# Generated example files (if auto-generated during pilot authoring)
examples/PLAN-EXAMPLE.md

# OS and editor noise
.DS_Store
*.swp
*~
